OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis revives staff   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbonus but warns of price   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frises                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, John Lewis has restored its annual     
OL,6, staff bonus after sales bounced back in
OL,7, 2021, but it warned customers would see
OL,8, higher prices this year.               
OL,10,FThe retailer scrapped bonuses last year
OL,11,Ffor the first time since 1953 after    
OL,12,Fseeing heavy losses in the pandemic.   
OL,14,FIt said sales at its department stores 
OL,15,Fhad since rebounded to a record #4.9bn,
OL,16,Fwhile revenues at its Waitrose         
OL,17,Fsupermarkets rose 1% to #7.5bn.        
OL,19,FBut it said it faced "significant" cost
OL,20,Fpressures it would have to pass on.    
